</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=promagi>ProMagi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#333333>(2/6/03 4:25:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm26.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=255.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: What do I say?</span><hr size=1> In another post someone lists all the Unique abilities of the epic vs. the standard nature of the post 60 pets and it makes all the sense in the world to still get the epic just for variety sake.<br>
<br>
Also lets not forget this. The epic is also a badge of achievement. And that is worth as much as the pet as far as I'm concerned.<br>
